{"tid":204951,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得依個假期條街少咗人","createTime":"2017-04-17T12:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T12:22:43.000Z","uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"383564d444348b33b3725cd0730310ab19a0485d","tid":204951,"uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:14:40.000Z","msg":"依個日落街條街好似少咗人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔單只係大陸人，好似連香港人都少咗好多咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明其他假期都唔會咁，或至上年嘅復活節都唔覺，有冇其他巴絲都一樣咁覺得，定話得我一個咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d713bd6c9f78557767756d3618be077a38e886","tid":204951,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:15:06.000Z","msg":"一連4日 多左人去旅行？"},{"pid":"15dcd58e8921bfad97e88c9abb98c3f2eca24104","tid":204951,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:16:14.000Z","msg":"大部份真香港人外遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8de10e835feaed942917f2d96d0af9f49b2b6473","tid":204951,"uid":20460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:16:55.000Z","msg":"應該去旅行 <br />\n一年有幾多長假呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e246f482256d83be63c3aee9b6cc6fc879d581d8","tid":204951,"uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:22:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該去旅行 <br />\n一年有幾多長假呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係聖誕同新年條街又好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋我身邊好多人都冇去遊行，所以覺得有啲奇點解咁少人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}